@startuml FlightStateDiagram
title Flight Object State Transition Diagram

[*] --> Scheduled : createFlight

state Scheduled
state Active
state Completed
state Cancelled

' --- Normal flow ---
Scheduled --> Active   : depart / startFlight
Active    --> Completed: arrive / endFlight

' --- Emergency termination flow ---
Active    --> Completed: emergencyLand / handleEmergencyLanding

' --- Cancellation only before departure ---
Scheduled --> Cancelled: cancel / cancelFlight

Completed --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]

@enduml
